Client for the cranchecks.info API

Scott Chamberlain

2020-05-19

Source: vignettes/cchecks.Rmd
cchecks.Rmd

cchecks is a client for the https://cranchecks.info API

Install

remotes::install_github("ropensci/cchecks")
library("cchecks")

cch_heartbeat()
